---
title: Cherry-Glazed Venison & Lemony Greens with Garlic-Parmesan Potatoes & Roasted Almonds
description: The sticky, sweetness of our cherry glaze really gets the mouth watering. Drizzled over tender seared venison steak and a side of herb infused potatoes, with roasted almonds, this completely luxe dish will make the average dinner feel like a special occasion.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6645a7a27f0f25a24185c836-618a12da.jpeg
